https://github.com/nrkn/SimpleRL

SimpleRL in Factor (http://factorcode.org/) by Risto Saarelma

This version uses the built-in Factor UI framework.

To run, copy the `simplerl` directory with `simplerl.factor` source file into
the `work/` subdirectory in your Factor directory tree, and type `"simplerl"
run` in the Factor listener.